metadata.name: The Barber
metadata.description:
The Barber

Always has a smile on his face 

His Spirit was contagious

The Joy he had 

Even during the days of the pandemic when the shop had to close temporarily

I ran into this man in a park and he still had joy 

Joy this thing we call joy 

is found, not by what we do , not by what we see, not by our circumstances, not by who we're around 

Joy comes from the Lord Jesus 

Many will see the joy in you
